It is listed at C$10,880,000.

Goodnight! 😍 This stunning English Tudor style stone home is located on Palm Royale Boulevard in Sugar Land, Texas. 

It was designed by Patrick Berrios Designs and built in 2017 by Sims Luxury Builders. It features over 11,000 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 6 full and 3 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, 2-story great room & dining room, gourmet kitchen with double islands, breakfast room, 2-story family room, home theater and more. 

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, fountain, porte-cochere, covered/uncovered patios, fireplace, kitchen/BBQ and a swimming pool with spa.

Photography by JONATHAN CALVERT 

(Not For Sale)

It was built in 2013 and features approximately 8,816 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 7 full and 2 half bathrooms, foyer, staircase, formal living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, 2 offices, bonus room with wet bar, home theater, 5-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrances, balconies & patios, fireplace, fire pit and an an enclosed kitchen.

It is listed at $3,500,000.

Goodnight! 😍 This newly built home is located at 3001 Inwood Drive in Houston, Texas and is situated on an acre of land.

It features approximately 12,095 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 7 full and 4 half bathrooms, foyer with staircase, elevator, great room, formal dining room with wine room, wet bar, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, paneled office/library, bonus room with wet bar, 4-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, balconies & patios, kitchen/BBQ and a swimming pool with spa.

It's listed at $16,500,000

Good morning! 😍 This newly built home is located at 1920 Pleasant Valley Road in West Bend, Wisconsin and is situated on 10 acres of land.

It features approximately 8,140 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 6 full and 1 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with staircase, 2-story great room, dining room, gourmet kitchen, separate prep kitchen, office, rec room with wet bar, home theater, gym, 12-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a deck, patio and a swimming pool.

It is listed at $2,999,900

node.text:
Goodnight! 😍 This modern home is located at 2738 Carina Way in Henderson, Nevada and is situated on nearly an acre of land.

It was built in 2017 and features approximately 14,207 square feet of living space with 4 bedrooms, 9 bathrooms, foyer with floating staircase & glass elevator, 2-story great room, living room with wet bar, dining room, gourmet kitchen, office, game room with wet bar, home theater, gym, lounge with indoor rock climbing wall, wine cellar, indoor half-court basketball court, 12-car garage with lift to the master suite and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, multiple balconies/patios, kitchen/BBQ, wet bar, infinity pool, spa, water & fire features and a putting green.

It's listed at $32,500,000

node.text:
Good morning! 😍 This French inspired limestone home, dubbed “Chateau de la Roche”, is located at 48 Rio Vista Drive, Alpine, New Jersey and is situated on 2 acres of land.

It was designed by Zampolin & Associates and built in 2017. It features approximately 25,700 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 12 bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, elevator, 2-story great room, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen with double islands, breakfast room, family room, 2-story conservatory, paneled home office/library, 15-seat home theater, billiards room, 2 wet bars, wine cellar, 2 indoor plunge pools, sauna, steam room, garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, balcony, patio, gazebo with BBQ/kitchen, swimming pool with spa, pool house and a fountain.

It's listed at $25,000,000
